OL,3,CInvestigation launched into 'missing
OL,4,Cashes' at funeral home
OL,6,FPolice have launched a probe into a
OL,7,Fformer funeral directors' company amid
OL,8,Fclaims of missing ashes.
OL,10,FForensics officers were seen going
OL,11,Finto a branch of A Milne Funeral
OL,12,FDirectors in Springburn, , after
OL,13,Fseveral families reported allegations
OL,14,Fof ashes going missing, and financial
OL,15,Fmisconduct.
OL,17,FThe firm also had a branch in
OL,18,FDumbarton, West Dunbartonshire, which
OL,19,Fhas since closed.
