OL,6,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"An investigation is ongoing into to
OL,8,Fthe conduct of a former funeral
OL,9,Fcompany that had branches in Glasgow
OL,10,Fand Dumbarton with regard to the
OL,11,Fstorage/return of cremated remains and
OL,12,Fallegations of financial misconduct.
OL,14,F"Inquiries are at an early stage."
