OL,6,FA post on Facebook announced the
OL,7,Fopening of the Springburn branch in
OL,8,F2019, which read: "At A Milne Funeral
OL,9,FDirectors, we are committed to
OL,10,Fproviding a dignified service with
OL,11,Fcourtesy and respect to your loved
OL,12,Fone. Our services are available at any
OL,13,Ftime, day or night with experienced
OL,14,Fstaff to help and assist you."
OL,16,FThe firm described itself as "an
OL,17,Findependent, family owned and operated
OL,18,Forganisation", and a post by a
OL,19,Fcustomer described it as a "father and
OL,20,Fdaughter business".
