OL,6,FThe director, Steve Milne, was born in
OL,7,F1967 and took up the position in
OL,8,FJanuary 2023, the same month that ex-
OL,9,Fdirector Ashleigh Milne, born in 1987,
OL,10,Fceased to be in the role, according to
OL,11,FCompanies House.
OL,13,FThe National Association of Funeral
OL,14,FDirectors (NAFD) has been contacted by
OL,15,Ffamilies.
OL,17,FA spokeswoman for the NAFD said: "We
OL,18,Fcan confirm that the NAFD has received
OL,19,Fa number of complaints about A Milne,
OL,20,Fwhich have been scrutinised by our
OL,21,Fcommittee for professional standards.
