OL,6,F"The firm appears to have stopped
OL,7,Fcorresponding with us, however, they
OL,8,Fhave been formally notified that they
OL,9,Fwill be considered by the NAFD
OL,10,Fdisciplinary committee at a meeting in
OL,11,FMay, where the ultimate sanction we
OL,12,Fhave at our disposal is removal from
OL,13,Fmembership.
OL,15,F"Under the terms of reference of the
OL,16,Fcommittee, we do not publicly disclose
OL,17,Fthe details of complaints made.
